
dressup-girl-pwa/
├── public/
│   ├── clothes/            ← all your dress images
│   ├── hair/               ← hairstyles
│   ├── makeup/             ← makeup overlays
│   ├── bg/                 ← bedroom background
│   └── base/               ← base character image
├── src/
│   └── App.jsx             ← the React game code
├── package.json            ← project info & dependencies
├── manifest.json           ← for offline support (PWA)
├── service-worker.js       ← caches files for offline use
└── index.html              ← main web page
